sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client/Frontend
  participant G as NGINX Gateway
  participant S as Source Service
  participant A as Analytics Service
  participant E as events collection
  participant P as projector.ts
  participant R as analytics read model

  C->>G: User action (book/forum/chat/admin)
  G->>S: Domain API call
  S->>A: POST /api/analytics/events
  A->>E: insert event
  A->>P: projectEvent(event)
  P->>R: upsert per-user aggregates
  A-->>S: { success: true }
  S-->>C: domain response
